Detourne existing images from its original function and use them in a new context, in a way to amplify the political meaning of the montage and to transform the cinema in a place of exchange of experiences: that was Guy DebordÂ´s project, taken again now, under new basis, by directors who work with archives images. This article analyses the detournment throught Debord films and writings and evaluates how up to date is the situacionist proposal. 
 
Keywords 
Debord. Coutinho. Detournement.